## Game Assets License

The following assets belong to Michael Ngo and are used here with permission for
non-commercial purposes:

- Lotus mascot character sprites (`lotus1.png` – `lotus9.png`)
- Logo (`logo.png`)
- Button artwork (`button_image.png`)
- Gift box (`gift_box.png`)
- Background image (`background1.jpg`)
- Loading bar elements (`loading_bar_*.png`)
- Curtain graphics (`curtain.png`)
- Audio tracks (`music.mp3`, `yay.mp3`)

### What you can do with the assets:
- ✅ Play the game
- ✅ Share and redistribute the game as-is (including assets)
- ✅ Use for personal, educational, or fan purposes

### What you cannot do with the assets:
- ❌ Modify or derivative works of the art/audio without permission
- ❌ Use the assets in commercial projects or for commercial gain
- ❌ Claim ownership of the VietMoney branding or artwork
- ❌ Sell or license the assets separately

